  <div class="col-md-10 col-sm-9">
    <h3>Our Goals</h3>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-9">
        <p> Sharing the human resource and allowing it to be accessed through the H.E.R.O Initiative will achieve these goals:</p>
        <ul>
          <li> Activities for social inclusion</li>
          <li> Intergenerational communications</li>
          <li> Communication between all socioeconomic groups, ethnicities and genders</li>
          <li> Increase knowledge base for participants </li>
          <li> Increase cultural sensitivity (make it a habit to be caring)</li>
          <li> Doing something tangible</li>
          <li> Provide choices (options for people to choose career or entrepreneurial)</li>
          <li> Increase civic engagement</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-3">
      </div>
    </div>
    <br><br>
  </div>
</div>
